channel.title: Prismuh 317 Experience
channel.description:
Prismuh
[size=12pt]Server Info[/size] Server Base: iClarity Server Client: Ambitionz 420 ( A little head start )
[size=12pt]Features[/size] - All 474 emotes (Including skillcapes) - All 474 interfaces - GFXs matching emotes 100%, perfect delays hits and all effects of current runescape. - Teleblock- 100% - Ancients - 100% - Modern - 100% - GodWars - Veng/Veng Other 100% - New Barrage method ( Can't move for a real good 15 seconds) - Multi Barrage - Full Woodcutting, Herborle, Cooking, Firemaking, [color=green]- Rushing 100%[/color] - Dragon Claws & Animation - Explock - Correct models - 63 waves & healers - Barbarian Assault - Pest Control - Add Magic Longbow special anim. - Give Magic Shortbow the GFX it is supposed to have. - Full Autocasting on PVN. - Fixed all sorts of dupes.
Pictures: [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/33a7a68.png[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/j7yy3t.png[/img] [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/1fadqg.gif[/img] Dragon Poisoning [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/ve901u.gif[/img] After Voting [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2wqrj80.png[/img]
[size=14pt] Lastest update[/size] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/14t4sqg.png[/img]
